Thanks for any suggestion. <br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uglenfinen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glenfinen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 122<br> <font color=#333333>(4/13/01 5:25:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=88.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: DAMMIT ! I hate hunting around FREEPORT!</span><hr size=1> Get in a group.<br>
<br>
Aside from that, you can go to east karana and kill snakes spiders and hounds.  Or just go thru the Nekultos forest along the left wall and fight stuff in Lavastorm mountains. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uteldivagrimleux.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teldiva GrimLeux</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/22/1603922.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 135<br> <font color=#333333>(4/13/01 6:53:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=88.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.facelink.com/edit/raw/image/59/3431759.jpg?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: DAMMIT ! I hate hunting around FREEPORT!</span><hr size=1> Depends on your goal.<br>
<br>
If you're a &quot;true newbie&quot;... as in this is your first character and you need good loot as well as exp, go to Lavastorm.  Same if you're solo.  Mages are great against summoned mobs.. make use of cancel magic and your dismiss summoned line of spells.<br>
<br>
If you're a twink.. as in this is an alternate character and you're just looking for fast leveling, get a good group of experienced players together and go to Kerra Island. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Don't laugh.  I know this is one of the least hunted areas in Norrath, but that's partly why it's so great.<br>
<br>
I am part of a &quot;weekly alt night&quot; group with a few of my guild members.  Our group consists of an enchanter, cleric, paladin, necromancer, druid, shadow knight.  Everyone in this group has high level main characters, so everything is done tactfully, and we are raking in the experience.  We are all in our high teens now and have already made it to the area right outside the Temple.. with little to no downtime, killing reds and yellows.  Of course exp is slowing down a bit now that we're rising in levels, but thus far we're averaging 1-3 levels per night, depending on how long we stay and how many CR's we have to do. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
In other words, Kerra can be very good experience with the right group.  Keep it in mind. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><center><img src=http://facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/61/1668561.jpg></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uezno.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ezno</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/posticons/eyes.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 394<br> <font color=#333333>(4/13/01 10:33:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=88.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: DAMMIT ! I hate hunting around FREEPORT!</span><hr size=1> <br>
I always loved going to East Karana during those levels.  EK/Gorge is great for 12-20th levels.   <br>
<br>
Getting in a group and going to Befallen is great if you are looking for fun.    <p> <br>
